<m0>UF to student doctors: Quit abortion clinics<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS .11 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .531 INCHES<m2><ql>
